<hymn_number>275</hymn_number>
<title>Dam Takin Chieh In !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungguol takin Lalpa, ka lennau tang chungah
 Kalvari tui hing ka dawnpih teu kha
 Chawmlo kalin lenna tang dang ding ahi.

[V2]
 Aw na chieh nang tuonglam sau mahleh lau loin
 Galhat Lalpa'n na ma pui ina
 Dam takin guol ngaih chiehin
 Lalpa vangsak in.

[V3]
 2. Aw na chieh lai ni chun Kraws chu bangmah lele
 Lalpa Thagau Thiengtho in hun pui ina
 Lungkhamna meipi leh gallien tawng zelin

[V4]
 3. Leia len-guol khen cheng Zion tang hawih chungah
 Ginnan I lengkhawm ui lung kipakin
 Hinna Thing leh ka Lalpa tha lim nuoiah.</lyrics>
</song>